      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Are you ready for your next great project? This car is in poor condition and will require some significant mechanical and cosmetic love, but it\u2019s a fantastic opportunity for a hands-on enthusiast to bring a vehicle back to life or use it for valuable parts. It\u2019s a budget-friendly way to get started on a rewarding restoration journey!",
