    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold strictly as-is. It requires significant mechanical and cosmetic attention before it can be considered roadworthy. The exterior shows heavy signs of wear, including deep scratches, dents, and significant paint fading. Mechanically, the engine and transmission need major repairs, and the interior has sustained considerable damage over time. This is a project car for someone with the tools and expertise to perform a full restoration or for use as a parts vehicle.",
