    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its ownership. The exterior retains a strong shine, though you may find a few minor stone chips and light surface scratches upon close inspection. Inside, the cabin is clean and comfortable, showing only minimal wear consistent with careful use. Mechanically, it runs smoothly and has a documented service history, making it a dependable choice for its next owner.",
