      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "This distinguished vehicle represents a premier opportunity for the discerning driver. Meticulously maintained and presenting in commendable condition, it offers a harmonious balance of performance and sophisticated aesthetics. Every component has been thoroughly vetted to ensure long-term mechanical integrity and road-ready reliability. We invite you to experience the refined engineering and enduring quality of this exceptional offering.",
